LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVJQ81656635920073_shipper_rate_last_date AS shipper_rate_last_date ON shipper_rate_last_date.id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_RATE_ID") and shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey > shipper_rate_last_date.date_skey 
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV1RF1656640736131_shipments_spot_last_60_days AS shipments_spot_last_60_days ON shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey = shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey 
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV4TI1656633972440_budget_product_daily AS budget_product_daily ON (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(budget_product_daily.actual_date ), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) = (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) 
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV48H1656636407988_shipments_actual AS shipments_actual ON shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey = shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey 
WHERE ((( shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE"  ) >= ((TO_TIMESTAMP('2022-01-01'))) AND ( shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE"  ) < ((DATEADD('year', 1, TO_TIMESTAMP('2022-01-01'))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('week', shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ))
ORDER BY
    1 DESC
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
